title: Episode 10 - Fletcher Greene of The Hollywood Fix
description:
The Hollywood Fix joins the podcast to talk about life as a TikTok paparazzi. The guys breakdown life in Miami over break, and what Nessa might think of it. We play Marry Fuck Kill, Boomer vs Zoomer, and get to your New Years questions.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/bffspod
